quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  9,81,Peefchay reh janey walay log rasool Allah (PBUH) kay janey kay baad apney bethay rehney per khush hain enhon ney Allah ki raah mein apney maal aur apni janon say jihad kerna na pasand rakha aur enhon ney keh diya kay iss garmi mein mat niklo. Keh dijiye kay dozakh ki aag boht hi sakht garam hai kaash kay woh samajhtay hotay
  9,82,Pus enhen chahaiye kay boht kum hansen aur boht ziyada royen badlay mein uss kay jo yeh kertay hain
  9,83,Pus agar Allah Taalaa aap ko inn ki kissi jamat ki taraf lota ker wapis ley aaye phir yeh aap say maidan-e-jang mein nikalney ki ijazat talab keren to aap keh dijiye kay tum meray hergiz chal nahi saktay aur na meray sath tum dushmanon say laraee ker saktay ho. Tum ney pehli martaba hi beth rehney ko pasand kiya tha pus tum peechay reh janey walon mein hi bethay raho
  9,84,Inn mein say koi marr jaye to aap uss kay janazay ki hergiz namaz na parhen aur na uss ki qabar per kharay hon. Yeh Allah aur uss kay rasool kay munkir hain aur martay dum tak bad kaar bey ita’at rahen hain
  9,85,Aap ko inn kay maal-o-aulad kuch bhi bhalay na lagen! Allah ki chahat yehi hai kay enhen inn cheezon say dunyawi saza dey aur yeh apni janen nikalney tak kafir hi rahen
  9,86,Jab koi surat utari jati hai kay Allah per eman lao aur uss kay rasool kay sath mill ker jihad kero to inn mein say dolat mandon kay aik tabqa aap kay pass aaker yeh keh ker rukhsat ley leta hai kay humen to bethay rehney walon mein hi chor chor dijiye
  9,87,Yeh to khana nasheen aurton ka sath denay per reejh gaye aur inn kay dilon per mohar laga di gaee abb woh kuch samajh aqal nahi rakhtay
  9,88,Lekin khud rasool Allah (PBUH) aur iss kay sath kay eman walay apney maalon aur janon say jihad kertay hain yehi log bhalaiyon walay hain aur yehi log kaamyabi hasil kerney walay hain
  9,89,Enhi kay liye Allah ney woh jannaten tayyar ki hain jin kay neechay nehren jaari hain jin mein yeh hamesha rehney walay hain yehi boht bari kaamyabi hai